Author: MissNietzsche
Text: I didn't used to when I was closer to 100% BED, but now that I've pretty much crossed ED territories, yep, this happens to me too. It literally only happens if I'm starving myself for prolonged periods of time though (I'm talking weeks/months). If I'm well fed, then fast for a week then binge, I won't get that awful feeling.
